        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[Requirements&#xA;]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_mojV" id="requirements"><a href="https://github.com/sonr-io/blockchain#requirements" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"></a>Requirements<a class="hash-link" href="#requirements" title="Direct link to heading">​</a></h3><ul><li><p><a href="https://golang.org/doc/install" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Go</a> installed on machine</p></li><li><p><a href="https://ignite.com/cli" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Ignite</a></p></li></ul><h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_mojV" id="steps-to-install-the-sonr-blockchain">Steps to install the Sonr Blockchain<a class="hash-link" href="#steps-to-install-the-sonr-blockchain" title="Direct link to heading">​</a></h3><h5 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_mojV" id="1-download-ignite">1. Download Ignite<a class="hash-link" href="#1-download-ignite" title="Direct link to heading">​</a></h5><div class="admonition admonition-tip alert alert--success"><div class="admonition-heading"><h5><span class="admonition-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="12" height="16" viewBox="0 0 12 16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6.5 0C3.48 0 1 2.19 1 5c0 .92.55 2.25 1 3 1.34 2.25 1.78 2.78 2 4v1h5v-1c.22-1.22.66-1.75 2-4 .45-.75 1-2.08 1-3 0-2.81-2.48-5-5.5-5zm3.64 7.48c-.25.44-.47.8-.67 1.11-.86 1.41-1.25 2.06-1.45 3.23-.02.05-.02.11-.02.17H5c0-.06 0-.13-.02-.17-.2-1.17-.59-1.83-1.45-3.23-.2-.31-.42-.67-.67-1.11C2.44 6.78 2 5.65 2 5c0-2.2 2.02-4 4.5-4 1.22 0 2.36.42 3.22 1.19C10.55 2.94 11 3.94 11 5c0 .66-.44 1.78-.86 2.48zM4 14h5c-.23 1.14-1.3 2-2.5 2s-2.27-.86-2.5-2z"></path></svg></span>tip</h5></div><div class="admonition-content"><div class="codeBlockContainer_I0IT language-shell theme-code-block"><div class="codeBlockContent_wNvx" style="color:#bfc7d5;background-color:#292d3e"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-shell codeBlock_jd64 thin-scrollbar"><code class="codeBlockLines_mRuA"><span class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token function" style="color:rgb(130, 170, 255)">curl</span><span class="token plain"> https://get.ignite.com/cli</span><span class="token operator" style="color:rgb(137, 221, 255)">!</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token operator" style="color:rgb(137, 221, 255)">|</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token function" style="color:rgb(130, 170, 255)">bash</span><br></span></code></pre><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="copyButton_eDfN clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_W9eQ" aria-hidden="true"><svg class="copyButtonIcon_XEyF" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_i9w9" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><h5 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_mojV" id="2-move-into-the-chain-directory">2. Move into the chain directory<a class="hash-link" href="#2-move-into-the-chain-directory" title="Direct link to heading">​</a></h5><div class="admonition admonition-tip alert alert--success"><div class="admonition-heading"><h5><span class="admonition-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="12" height="16" viewBox="0 0 12 16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6.5 0C3.48 0 1 2.19 1 5c0 .92.55 2.25 1 3 1.34 2.25 1.78 2.78 2 4v1h5v-1c.22-1.22.66-1.75 2-4 .45-.75 1-2.08 1-3 0-2.81-2.48-5-5.5-5zm3.64 7.48c-.25.44-.47.8-.67 1.11-.86 1.41-1.25 2.06-1.45 3.23-.02.05-.02.11-.02.17H5c0-.06 0-.13-.02-.17-.2-1.17-.59-1.83-1.45-3.23-.2-.31-.42-.67-.67-1.11C2.44 6.78 2 5.65 2 5c0-2.2 2.02-4 4.5-4 1.22 0 2.36.42 3.22 1.19C10.55 2.94 11 3.94 11 5c0 .66-.44 1.78-.86 2.48zM4 14h5c-.23 1.14-1.3 2-2.5 2s-2.27-.86-2.5-2z"></path></svg></span>tip</h5></div><div class="admonition-content"><div class="codeBlockContainer_I0IT language-shell theme-code-block"><div class="codeBlockContent_wNvx" style="color:#bfc7d5;background-color:#292d3e"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-shell codeBlock_jd64 thin-scrollbar"><code class="codeBlockLines_mRuA"><span class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token builtin class-name" style="color:rgb(255, 203, 107)">cd</span><span class="token plain"> blockchain</span><br></span></code></pre><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="copyButton_eDfN clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_W9eQ" aria-hidden="true"><svg class="copyButtonIcon_XEyF" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_i9w9" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><h5 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_mojV" id="3-serve-the-blockchain">3. Serve the blockchain<a class="hash-link" href="#3-serve-the-blockchain" title="Direct link to heading">​</a></h5><div class="admonition admonition-tip alert alert--success"><div class="admonition-heading"><h5><span class="admonition-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="12" height="16" viewBox="0 0 12 16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6.5 0C3.48 0 1 2.19 1 5c0 .92.55 2.25 1 3 1.34 2.25 1.78 2.78 2 4v1h5v-1c.22-1.22.66-1.75 2-4 .45-.75 1-2.08 1-3 0-2.81-2.48-5-5.5-5zm3.64 7.48c-.25.44-.47.8-.67 1.11-.86 1.41-1.25 2.06-1.45 3.23-.02.05-.02.11-.02.17H5c0-.06 0-.13-.02-.17-.2-1.17-.59-1.83-1.45-3.23-.2-.31-.42-.67-.67-1.11C2.44 6.78 2 5.65 2 5c0-2.2 2.02-4 4.5-4 1.22 0 2.36.42 3.22 1.19C10.55 2.94 11 3.94 11 5c0 .66-.44 1.78-.86 2.48zM4 14h5c-.23 1.14-1.3 2-2.5 2s-2.27-.86-2.5-2z"></path></svg></span>tip</h5></div><div class="admonition-content"><div class="codeBlockContainer_I0IT language-shell theme-code-block"><div class="codeBlockContent_wNvx" style="color:#bfc7d5;background-color:#292d3e"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-shell codeBlock_jd64 thin-scrollbar"><code class="codeBlockLines_mRuA"><span class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">ignite chain serve</span><br></span></code></pre><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="copyButton_eDfN clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_W9eQ" aria-hidden="true"><svg class="copyButtonIcon_XEyF" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_i9w9" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><ul><li><p>This is the command that starts the blockchain.</p></li><li><p>By adding the flag --reset-once it will reset the blockchain on the first startup</p></li></ul><h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_mojV" id="sonr-highway-sdk">Sonr Highway-SDK<a class="hash-link" href="#sonr-highway-sdk" title="Direct link to heading">​</a></h2><h4 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_mojV" id="installation-">Installation<!-- --> <a class="hash-link" href="#installation-" title="Direct link to heading">​</a></h4><ul><li>Install and run the Sonr Blockchain using the above guide</li></ul><h4 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_mojV" id="clone-the-highway-sdk-repo">Clone the Highway-SDK repo<a class="hash-link" href="#clone-the-highway-sdk-repo" title="Direct link to heading">​</a></h4><div class="codeBlockContainer_I0IT language-shell theme-code-block"><div class="codeBlockContent_wNvx" style="color:#bfc7d5;background-color:#292d3e"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-shell codeBlock_jd64 thin-scrollbar"><code class="codeBlockLines_mRuA"><span class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token function" style="color:rgb(130, 170, 255)">git</span><span class="token plain"> clone https://github.com/sonr-io/highway-sdk.git</span><br></span></code></pre><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="copyButton_eDfN clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_W9eQ" aria-hidden="true"><svg class="copyButtonIcon_XEyF" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_i9w9" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div><h4 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_mojV" id="run-the-highway-sdk-in-place">Run the Highway-SDK in place<a class="hash-link" href="#run-the-highway-sdk-in-place" title="Direct link to heading">​</a></h4><div class="codeBlockContainer_I0IT language-shell theme-code-block"><div class="codeBlockContent_wNvx" style="color:#bfc7d5;background-color:#292d3e"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-shell codeBlock_jd64 thin-scrollbar"><code class="codeBlockLines_mRuA"><span class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">go run main.go serve</span><br></span></code></pre><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="copyButton_eDfN clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_W9eQ" aria-hidden="true"><svg class="copyButtonIcon_XEyF" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_i9w9" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div><h4 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_mojV" id="add-more-building-blocks-with-the-cli">Add more building blocks with the CLI<a class="hash-link" href="#add-more-building-blocks-with-the-cli" title="Direct link to heading">​</a></h4><div class="codeBlockContainer_I0IT language-shell theme-code-block"><div class="codeBlockContent_wNvx" style="color:#bfc7d5;background-color:#292d3e"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-shell codeBlock_jd64 thin-scrollbar"><code class="codeBlockLines_mRuA"><span class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">go run main.go </span><span class="token operator" style="color:rgb(137, 221, 255)">&lt;</span><span class="token plain">serve/</span><span class="token operator" style="color:rgb(137, 221, 255)">&gt;</span><br></span></code></pre><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="copyButton_eDfN clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_W9eQ" aria-hidden="true"><svg class="copyButtonIcon_XEyF" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z"></path></svg><svg class="copyButtonSuccessIcon_i9w9" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div>]]></content>
